{"tid":1766901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共和黨列名單 制裁六人幫","createTime":"2019-12-03T02:33:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T11:21:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"797ad91cfd9f3a946b4c2b33ad22c5ddb8c951c0","tid":1766901,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T02:33:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191203/YEEOMP2IXVO5735NIA7GLCPUAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191203%2FYEEOMP2IXVO5735NIA7GLCPUAM%2F&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=802040c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191203%2FYEEOMP2IXVO5735NIA7GLCPUAM%2F&h=a624073b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191203/YEEOMP2IXVO5735NIA7GLCPUAM/</a><br />\n<br />\n共和黨列名單 制裁六人幫<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國通過《香港人權與民主法案》後，總統特朗普須依法訂定制裁名單，前日共和黨海外事務組織副主席俞懷松（Solomon Yue）在Twitter發文，列出制裁名單的「香港六人幫」，當中以特首林鄭月娥居首，行政會議成員葉劉淑儀亦有份。香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒接受訪問時表示，華府雖未有確實名單，但已開始就制裁目標人物層級作討論。<br />\n<br />\n俞懷松前日在Twitter發文，公佈聲稱來自「外洩制裁名單」六個香港官員及政客名字，稱為「六人幫」（Gang of Six），計有特首林鄭月娥、律政司長鄭若驊、多次出言撐警惹眾怒的保安局長李家超、剛卸任的警務處前處長盧偉聰、被指與元朗鄉黑關係密切的新警務處長鄧炳強，以及俞懷松戲稱「第一好朋友」的行會成員兼新民黨主席葉劉淑儀。<br />\n<br />\n根據《香港人權與民主法案》，美國總統須制訂制裁名單，懲治侵蝕香港自治和法治的人，包括拒絕入境美國、凍結在美資產等。葉劉昨批評港人大多抱「八卦」心態關注《人權法》，直指大眾純為發洩私怨，「非常可惜，眼光狹窄、短淺」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191203/large/1575303762_51f6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191203%2Flarge%2F1575303762_51f6.gif&h=0075b8a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美已就制裁目標作討論<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：Be Water法案將交委員會表決<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒接受本報查詢時稱，據從華府方面了解，現時仍未有確實名單，但當地行政機關已就制裁目標人物的層級作內部討論，「係特首？定司、局長級官員，定係高級公務員呢？當中都涉及現實政治考慮同可行程度，習近平都有打壓香港人權，但唔會制裁佢」。<br />\n<br />\n■記者陳珏明"},{"pid":"4050baaca93f81f93f45a7be333bd9fc0bfb7c5f","tid":1766901,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T02:37:34.000Z","msg":"［twitter戰線］美國嘈緊中共網絡監控同滲透<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1766812\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1766812</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRZKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=b2aa1f9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> /task2</span></span> 攞Tweets"},{"pid":"400d928c69d08806cf735d7ecb020ca14adfb283","tid":1766901,"uid":62247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T02:39:10.000Z","msg":"Best friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a76d4db67590fad2afa00fb2dd826f877fbc9f5","tid":1766901,"uid":205469,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T02:43:48.000Z","msg":"姐姐其實有d無辜<br />\n最多係幫兇<br />\n係衰多口"},{"pid":"6b21ef424bf94bafab2d8bba0adf0d7040419bce","tid":1766901,"uid":181088,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"2a76d4db67590fad2afa00fb2dd826f877fbc9f5","tid":1766901,"uid":205469,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T02:43:48.000Z","msg":"姐姐其實有d無辜<br />\n最多係幫兇<br />\n係衰多口"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T02:50:14.000Z","msg":"痴線 做得行會成員<br />\n收得份人工<br />\n但又想冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1db07820b2a4e057c45025c9047f793a77c28f40","tid":1766901,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T02:52:09.000Z","msg":"tweet"},{"pid":"bcefb5957858bdcab0125416f2f72b9cbcb7a79c","tid":1766901,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T02:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img sr